raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: Hey, almost ready!
Suzanna: No rush, and thank you again 😊
Suzanna: Sorry about the dress code as well
Player: No problem!
Suzanna: I have one additional request, if you would hear me out 🙂
Suzanna: But don't feel pressured to accept this request
Player: Sure, what is it?
Suzanna: Would you accompany me to a hotel after the date?
Player: 😳
Suzanna: Don't worry 😊
Suzanna: I've already arranged two separate rooms for us
Suzanna: You're free to leave after arriving, or if you'd like, you can stay in the fancy room!
Suzanna: But no need to feel like you have to be present around me
Player: Is this for the rumor business?
Suzanna: Quite ☹️ I found out one of my colleagues is on a date in the same restaurant 😓
Suzanna: So I thought this was the best opportunity to create the impression that things were going \"well\" 😊
Player: Ah, must mean a lot to you
Suzanna: Sorry for dragging you into my personal affairs, I must seem very unprofessional
Suzanna: But I don't know how I could ever repay you
if Story.orange_heart >= 3:
	Suzanna: Oh
	Suzanna: I could give you a little peek
	Suzanna: Last time you were receptive to a picture so it's the least I can do
	Suzanna: img: suzanna/9
	Suzanna: Maybe this is a little more appealing than formal wear? 🙊
	- You look great
		Player: You look great
		Suzanna: You flatter me 😊
	- My imagination is running wild right now [#orangeheart]
		set Story.orange_heart += 1
		Player: My imagination is running wild right now
		Suzanna: Oh my, is it now
	Suzanna: Oh dear, if you were only my age 😮‍💨
do advance_time(2, 20)
Suzanna: Are you settled comfortably in your room?
Player: Yeah this bed is huge lol 😁
Suzanna: Consider it a gift for today!
Suzanna: It's the least I could do
Suzanna: You wouldn't mind if I post the images from today on my social media?
Suzanna: img: suzanna/10
Suzanna: This one in particular is quite lovely
Player: Of course not
Suzanna: Thank you! 😊
Suzanna: My, I even look like a bit more youthful
- You have a pretty smile
	Player: You have a pretty smile
	Suzanna: How sweet of you to say
	Suzanna: You're such a charmer
- I liked your dress
	Player: I liked your dress
	Suzanna: I've had this old bag for a while now 😄
	Suzanna: But thank you
Suzanna: You really know how to treat a lady
- Would you mind sharing your social with me?
	Player: Would you mind sharing your social scene with me?
	Suzanna: Of course! 
	Suzanna: I don't usually share it with students so keep it between us 😇
	set PhoneUnlocks.reveal = \"suzanna\"
- Glad to hear it
	Player: Glad to hear it
Suzanna: I had a spectacular time
do social_post(\"suzanna_dinner_date\")
Suzanna: Did it have to be over so soon?
- It's not over yet [#orangeheart] [if Story.orange_heart >= 4]
	set Story.orange_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Suzanna1a\"
	Player: It's not over yet
	Suzanna: You're right, it might not be
	Suzanna: I suppose we can chat a bit
	Suzanna: You must be quite lucky with girls
	Suzanna: Showing them a great time like this
	- I consider myself lucky!
		Player: I consider myself lucky!
		Suzanna: Humble and cute
		Suzanna: Mabel is quite lucky too, isn't she
		Suzanna: I wish I had that kind of luck in my best days
	- Not as much as you'd think
		Player: Not as much as you'd think
		Suzanna: Really?
		Suzanna: I would have assumed a tall handsome young man like yourself would have an easy time in college
		Suzanna: But now you're reminding me of my own experience 🙊
	Player: Why, what happened?
	Suzanna: Well let's just say all my friends are married to their college sweethearts 😅
	Suzanna: And I was left out
	Player: You didn't have a boyfriend?
	Suzanna: I did but... I'd rather not be reminded 😞
	Player: My bad 😕
	Suzanna: No! It's my fault
	Suzanna: Sorry for dumping that on you
	Player: It's okay
	Suzanna: I've just had a lot of difficulty finding anyone who'd like to be serious with me since then
	Suzanna: Even now, I do what I can to reach out but it seems like at this age, everyone is just a playboy
	Suzanna: It's almost like all the good men are gone
	Player: Sounds really rough 😥
	Suzanna: IT IS!!
	Suzanna: I'd like to have kids too but I constantly feel under pressure with work, and my time too
	Suzanna: It's really stressful.. Will I be alone forever? 🥺
	Suzanna: Oh my, what am I saying
	Suzanna: That's a bit of the alcohol talking, excuse me for being so frank
	Player: No, it's okay!
	Suzanna: I'm just feeling really lonely
	Suzanna: Even now
	Suzanna: img: suzanna/11
	- It's lonely for me too
		Player: It's lonely for me too
		Suzanna: 😳
	- Maybe I can cheer you up
		Player: Maybe I can cheer you up
		Suzanna: Maybe.. you can
	Suzanna: Maybe you could come to my room, just... for a little bit
	Suzanna: For tonight, we can be a little less lonely together?
	Player: I'd like that
	Suzanna: I don't want the night to end on such a sour note
	Suzanna: Give me some time to prepare
	Player: Prepare what?
	Suzanna: This
	Suzanna: img: suzanna/12
	Player: 😳
	Suzanna: In about 15 minutes, knock 3 times on my door
	Player: Okay
- I'm glad you had a good time
	Player: I'm glad you had a good time
	Suzanna: I really did!
	Suzanna: You've uplifted my spirits and gave me some much needed confidence
	Suzanna: This should also help hold off the rumors for the meanwhile
	Player: Glad to help
	Suzanna: Good night sweetheart!
	Player: Good night 🙂
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
